data.title: JD Hayworth Archives
data.text:
J.D. Hayworth fills in for Vince. J.D. discusses Covid restrictions and President Biden’s push for Americans to get another round of Covid shots. Also, Ron DeSantis addresses the media on the potential dangers posed by Hurricane Idalia. That and much more on The Vince Coakley Radio Program. Listen Here:

J.D. Hayworth fills in for Vince. Rep. Dan Bishop joins the program to talk Biden corruption and a potential impeachment for President Joe Biden. More on the indictment of Donald Trump. Also, J.D. takes your calls during “Sound Off, Charlotte!” That and much more on The Vince Coakley Radio Program. Listen Here:

Former President Donald Trump has been indicted by a NY grand jury. The Hill has more: Former President Trump was indicted by a Manhattan grand jury Thursday, making history as the first executive — sitting or former — to face criminal charges. The indictment comes after District Attorney Alvin Bragg (D) initiated a probe investigating Trump’s involvement in organizing hush […]

Vince is off until Monday, so JD Hayworth fills in. JD fills you in on the latest news. Listen Here:

JD Hayworth is filling in for Vince. JD talks about the attack on 2nd amendment rights. Plus, more information coming out of the tragic Nashville school shooting. Listen Here:

Tragedy strikes again. This time a school shooting at a private Christian school in Nashville Tennessee. JD breaks down President Joe Biden’s comments on the shooting. Also, Donald Trump appears on FOX News in an interview with Sean Hannity. Listen Here:

JD discusses the fentanyl crisis plaguing the country and Joe Biden reacts to comments by a grieving mother who lost two kids to fentanyl overdose. More on the investigation into Twitter’s media bias. Thom Tillis joins CNN to chime in on Tucker Carlson’s coverage of J6. Plus, comments from Dr. Fauci on the origins of Covid. […]

Title 42 is set to expire in the next couple of days. J.D. looks at the effects this may have at the southern border.
